{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/OOL_StartScreenGif.gif?t=1739000292\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Oaths of Light</strong> is an <strong>adventure</strong> game <strong>inspired by modern and classic JRPGs</strong>, with a battle system <strong>mixing real-time and turn-based</strong>, <strong>choice</strong> and consequences systems, in a story-rich fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2022 Engaging turn-based battles with real-time elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The battle system is inspired by JRPG classics: <strong>turn-based</strong> battles with ordered turns and a <strong>twist</strong>. You have a <strong>five-second</strong> window during your turn to move, attack, use items, or cast skills. You can defend against enemy attacks by timing your blocks correctly, as long as the attacks are not from behind making positioning important.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/OOL_Battles_Gif.gif?t=1739000292\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2022 A beautiful, handcrafted world to explore with a fixed camera system</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of Oaths of Light is a <strong>colorful</strong> and <strong>vibrant fantasy</strong> one, but also full of <strong>magic</strong> and <strong>mysteries</strong>. Accompany Eden as she embarks on a journey to the capital to participate in the ceremonies of the <strong>Oaths of Light</strong>. Many events will occur prior and following this journey that will changer her forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/OOL_Steam_MovingAround.gif?t=1739000292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2022 Make choices and face their consequences</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout your journey, there will be occasions where you must <strong>make choices</strong> that will directly <strong>influence the storyline</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/OOL_Choices.gif?t=1739000292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/steam_steamermode_ENG.png?t=1739000292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/oolseparator.png?t=1739000292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549990/extras/ool_history.png?t=1739000292\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oaths of Light is set in <strong>Meadran</strong>. A world still recovering from a recent <strong>war</strong> that opposed the <strong>kingdom of Meadran</strong> and the <strong>Elmeians</strong>, people of the forest. At the heart of this conflict: <strong>Magic</strong>. In fact, a new usage for magic as a <strong>source of energy</strong> was discovered. And both sides fearing what a bad usage of such power could lead to started a race for power until an armed conflict happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our story takes place <strong>eleven years after</strong> the war ended. Scars from it are still fresh, and the <strong>winners</strong>, <strong>the Kingdom of Meadran</strong>, have established rules and strict control for the use of magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything begins at <strong>Reimber Village</strong>, the peaceful home of our main character. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A trou